      <hedline>
        <hl1>This Call's for You</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Alan Peres letter on using cell phone earbuds (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Your article missed an important practical use for cell phone earbuds. They make using phone mail and interactive voice response systems easy. When I use my cell phone without the bud, it is extremely inconvenient to shift the phone from my ear to my line of sight over and over as I struggle between listening to prompts and entering information. I often miss things as a result.</p>
        <p>ALAN PERES  Deerfield, Ill.</p>
      </block>
